268
00:22:00,583 --> 00:22:02,585
If you'll excuse me, sir.

269
00:22:10,509 --> 00:22:13,846
I'm afraid, sir, I must ask you
for the key and the recall code.

270
00:22:13,929 --> 00:22:15,681
Have you got them handy, sir?

271
00:22:15,765 --> 00:22:18,184
I told you to take it easy,
Group Captain.

272
00:22:18,267 --> 00:22:20,853
There's nothing anybody
can do about this thing now.

273
00:22:20,936 --> 00:22:23,356
I'm the only person who knows
the three-letter code group.

274
00:22:23,439 --> 00:22:26,108
Then I must insist, sir,
that you give them to me.

275
00:22:35,117 --> 00:22:39,246
Do I take it, sir, that you are threatening
