276
00:22:40,456 --> 00:22:42,458
Mandrake,

277
00:22:42,541 --> 00:22:45,127
I suppose it never occurred to you

278
00:22:45,711 --> 00:22:48,297
that while we're chatting here so enjoyably,

279
00:22:49,256 --> 00:22:52,385
