no possibility of recalling the wing,

282
00:23:03,229 --> 00:23:06,315
there will be only
one course of action open.

283
00:23:07,400 --> 00:23:09,235
Total commitment.

284
00:23:11,654 --> 00:23:16,325
Mandrake, do you recall what
Clemenceau once said about war?

285
