292
00:23:41,183 --> 00:23:42,935
the training

293
00:23:43,018 --> 00:23:45,938
nor the inclination for strategic thought.

294
00:23:49,817 --> 00:23:52,361
I can no longer sit back and allow

295
00:23:53,362 --> 00:23:55,614
Communist infiltration,

296
00:23:55,698 --> 00:23:57,533
Communist indoctrination,

297
00:23:58,534 --> 00:24:00,453
Communist subversion

298
00:24:01,662 --> 00:24:04,748
and the international Communist conspiracy

299
00:24:05,749 --> 00:24:08,461
to sap and impurify

300
00:24:08,544 --> 00:24:11,630
all of our precious bodily fluids.

301
00:24:18,137 --> 00:24:19,805
Staines, is everybody here?

302
00:24:19,889 --> 00:24:22,183
Mr. President,
