just as soon as he can.

424
00:31:12,634 --> 00:31:13,719
All right.

425
00:31:13,802 --> 00:31:16,972
Listen, shug, don't forget
to say your prayers.

426
00:31:24,354 --> 00:31:26,398
Apparently,

427
00:31:26,481 --> 00:31:29,651
the 23rd Airborne Division
is stationed seven miles away

428
00:31:29,735 --> 00:31:31,236
at Alvarado.

429
00:31:31,320 --> 00:31:34,406
General Faceman,
I want them to enter the base,

430
00:31:34,489 --> 00:31:37,951
locate General Ripper and put him
in immediate telephone contact with me.

431
00:31:38,035 --> 00:31:39,536
Yes, sir.

432
00:31:39,620 --> 00:31:42,915
Mr. President, if I may advise,

433
00:31:42,998 --> 00:31:45,375
under condition red,
it is standard procedure

434
00:31:45,459 --> 00:31:47,377
that the base be sealed off

435
00:31:47,461 --> 00:31:50,130
and the base defended
by base security troops.

436
00:31:50,213 --> 00:31:54,176
Any force trying to enter there would
certainly encounter very heavy casualties.

437
00:31:54,968 --> 00:31:59,097
General Turgidson, with all due respect
for your defense team,

438
00:31:59,181 --> 00:32:01,683
my boys can brush 'em aside
without too much trouble.

439
00:32:02,559 --> 00:32:07,439
Mr. President, there are one or two points
I'd like to make if I may.

440
00:32:08,357 --> 00:32:09,858
Go ahead, General.

441
00:32:11,360 --> 00:32:15,948
One, our hopes for recalling
the 843rd Bomb Wing

442
00:32:16,031 --> 00:32:20,452
are quickly being reduced
to a very low order of probability.

443
00:32:20,535 --> 00:32:23,330
Two, in less than 15 minutes from now

444
00:32:23,413 --> 00:32:26,541
the Russkies will be making
radar contact with the planes.

445
00:32:26,625 --> 00:32:30,420
Three, when they do
they are gonna go absolutely ape

446
00:32:30,504 --> 00:32:32,664
and they're gonna strike back
with everything they got.

447
00:32:32,923 --> 00:32:36,259
Four, if, prior to this time,

448
00:32:36,343 --> 00:32:39,763
we have done nothing further
to suppress their retaliatory capabilities,

449
00:32:39,846 --> 00:32:42,975
