01:00:53,163 --> 01:00:56,041
I'll take that for you, Jack.
And you know what I'm hoping, Jack?

879
01:00:56,124 --> 01:00:59,169
I'm hoping you're going to give me
the code, boy, that's what I'm hoping.

880
01:00:59,252 --> 01:01:02,964
You're going to have a little wash
