881
01:01:03,048 --> 01:01:06,051
Always did wonders for a man that, Jack.
A little wash and brush up.

882
01:01:06,134 --> 01:01:08,512
Water on the back of the neck.
Makes you feel marvelous.

883
01:01:08,595 --> 01:01:11,848
That's what we need, Jack.
Water on the back of the neck and the code.

884
01:01:11,932 --> 01:01:14,184
Supposing I play a little guessing game
with you, Jack boy.

885
01:01:14,267 --> 01:01:16,853
I'll try and guess,
I'll try and guess what the code is.

