1081
01:14:54,545 --> 01:14:58,591
and remaining fuel 8790.

1082
01:15:05,097 --> 01:15:09,143
No. No, Dmitri,
there must be some mistake.

1083
01:15:09,227 --> 01:15:11,270
No, I'm certain of that.

1084
01:15:11,354 --> 01:15:13,773
I'm perfectly certain of that, Dmitri.

1085
01:15:15,650 --> 01:15:17,485
Just a second.

1086
01:15:17,568 --> 01:15:20,905
You know what he says? He says that
one of the planes hasn't turned back.

1087
01:15:20,988 --> 01:15:23,699
He says, according to information
forwarded by our air staffs,

1088
01:15:23,783 --> 01:15:26,452
it's headed for the missile complex
at Laputa.

1089
01:15:30,706 --> 01:15:32,708
That's impossible, Mr. President.

1090
01:15:32,792 --> 01:15:34,710
I mean, look at the big board.

1091
01:15:34,794 --> 01:15:38,214
Thirty-four planes. 30 recalls
acknowledged and four splashes,

1092
01:15:38,297 --> 01:15:40,800
and one of them
was targeted for Laputa.

1093
01:15:43,761 --> 01:15:46,889
Dmitri? Look, we've got
an acknowledgement from every plane

1094
01:15:46,973 --> 01:15:49,141
except the four you shot down.

1095
01:15:57,108 --> 01:15:59,860
He... Hang on a second, Dmitri.

1096
01:15:59,944 --> 01:16:03,322
He says their air defense now
only claims three aircraft confirmed.

1097
01:16:03,406 --> 01:16:05,491
The fourth may only be damaged.

1098
01:16:07,994 --> 01:16:12,748
Mr. President, I'm beginning
to smell a big fat commie rat.

1099
01:16:12,832 --> 01:16:16,627
I mean, supposing Kissoff
is lying about that fourth plane,

1100
01:16:16,711 --> 01:16:18,629
just looking for an excuse
to clobber us?

1101
01:16:18,713 --> 01:16:22,258
I mean, if the spaghetti hits the fan,
now we're really in trouble.

1102
01:16:25,595 --> 01:16:31,517
Dmitri? Look, if this report is true
and the plane manages to bomb the target,

1103
01:16:31,601 --> 01:16:33,603
is this... is this going to

1104
01:16:33,686 --> 01:16:35,938
is this going to set off
the Doomsday Machine?

1105
01:16:39,025 --> 01:16:40,943
Are you sure?

1106
01:16:42,486 --> 01:16:46,866
Well, I guess you're just going
to have to get that plane, Dmitri.

1107
01:16:46,949 --> 01:16:50,119
Dmitri, I'm sorry they're jamming
your radar and flying so low,

1108
01:16:50,202 --> 01:16:51,746
but they're trained to do it.

1109
01:16:51,829 --> 01:16:53,539
It's initiative.

1110
01:16:55,625 --> 01:16:58,794
Look, Dmitri, you know
exactly where they're going,

1111
01:16:58,878 --> 01:17:02,882
and I'm sure your entire air defense
can stop a single plane.

1112
01:17:04,258 --> 01:17:07,178
Listen, I mean, it's not gonna
help either one of us

1113
01:17:07,261 --> 01:17:10,931
if the Doomsday Machine goes off,
now, is it?

1114
01:17:11,015 --> 01:17:16,479
Dmitri, there's no point in you
getting hysterical at a moment like this.

1115
01:17:16,562 --> 01:17:20,983
Dmitri, keep your feet on the ground
when you're talking, Dmitri.

1116
01:17:21,067 --> 01:17:23,152
I am not... I am not getting...

1117
01:17:23,235 --> 01:17:27,323
No, Dmitri, I'm just worried, that's all.

1118
01:17:27,406 --> 01:17:30,701
Now look, if our air staff say
its primary target is Laputa

1119
