and its secondary target is Barchov,

1120
01:17:32,912 --> 01:17:36,165
I mean, it's true, Dmitri,
you've got to believe it.

1121
01:17:36,248 --> 01:17:39,960
Look, can I give... Dmitri?
Can I give you just one word...

1122
01:17:40,044 --> 01:17:43,255
Can I give you just one word
of advice, Dmitri?

1123
01:17:43,339 --> 01:17:48,761
Listen, Dmitri, put everything you've got
into those two sectors and you can't miss.

1124
01:17:55,142 --> 01:17:58,813
Sir, if we continue
to lose fuel at the present rate,

