1145
01:19:26,859 --> 01:19:28,778
Well, we'll keep our fingers crossed,
Dmitri,

1146
01:19:28,861 --> 01:19:31,739
and remember, there's just one thing,
we are all in this together.

1147
01:19:31,822 --> 01:19:35,576
We're right behind you, Dmitri.
We're with you all the way.

1148
01:19:35,659 --> 01:19:38,287
Yes, well, we'll keep the line open.

